title: Why is my Twitter account in a superposition state?
text: Trying to use an account I created a long time ago. Logging in with the old password fails. Attempts to reset the password using my email produce "Sorry we could not find your account". Meanwhile an attempt to create a new account with my email produces "Email has already been taken".
